---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Malik Fajar Mubarok">
  <header class="site-header">
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="nav-home">Malik Fajar Mubarok</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="nav-link">Blog</a>
      <a href="/cv" class="nav-link">CV</a>
      <a href="/cats" class="nav-link">Cats</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="home">
    <section class="intro">
      <h1>Hi, I'm Malik Fajar Mubarok</h1>
      <p>A data professional with 7+ years of experience building scalable data platforms, distributed pipelines, and production data workflows.</p>
      <p>I work primarily with Python, SQL, and cloud ecosystems (GCP, AWS), with a focus on orchestration and modern analytics engineering practices.</p>
      <p>Currently pursuing a Master's degree in AI to deepen my understanding of machine learning and intelligent systems.</p>
      <p><b>My research topic:</b> instruction tuning of a vision-language model (Gemma 3) for culturally-aware Indonesian image captioning.</p>
      <p>This site is where I document my work, explorations, and anything in between.</p>
      <a href="/blog" class="read-blog">Read my blog →</a>

      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/malikfm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="LinkedIn" class="social-icon">
